OL,3,C'Bold measures' needed to tackle surge
OL,4,Cin formula milk costs, report says
OL,6,FThe rising cost of formula milk is
OL,7,Fhaving a "devastating" effect on
OL,8,Ffamilies and forcing them into "tough
OL,9,Fchoices" to feed their babies,
OL,10,Faccording to a report.
OL,12,FSome 65% of women surveyed for the
OL,13,FBritish Pregnancy Advisory Service
OL,14,F(BPAS) said they felt anxious or
OL,15,Fworried about the cost of formula,
OL,16,Fwhich has risen by 25% over the last
OL,17,Ftwo years.
OL,19,FThe same percentage reported a
OL,20,Fnegative impact on family finances as
OL,21,Fa result of the cost.
